data.description: This cozy 3 bed 2.5 bath colonial style home is ready for you! Vinyl plank flooring throughout the home, full basement, sliding doors to deck and a beautiful covered front porch. The kitchen is VERY spacious, stainless steal appliances with a dining area. Everything is NEW! Bedrooms are spacious with plenty of storage space in closets and carpeted. Level and large back yard is ready for kids, dogs, garden, or cookouts! Conveniently located by many stores and restaurants, and close to I-81!. You cannot go wrong with this home, hurry before its gone!
